ZH: 我喜欢运动。
EN: I like doing sports.
ZH: 她每天都会参加户外运动。
EN: She participates in outdoor activities every day.
ZH: 他因为运动而很健康。
EN: He is very healthy because of exercise.
ZH: 运动可以帮助放松身心。
EN: Exercise can help relax the body and mind.
ZH: 周末我们会和朋友一起运动。
EN: We will exercise with friends on the weekend.
ZH: 每周我都会去健身房锻炼身体。
EN: I go to the gym to exercise every week.
ZH: 运动可以提高免疫力。
EN: Exercise can boost immunity.
ZH: 做适量的运动有助于减肥。
EN: Doing moderate exercise can help with weight loss.
ZH: 运动可以促进血液循环。
EN: Exercise can promote blood circulation.
ZH: 每天做一些运动对你的心脏很有好处。
EN: Doing some exercise every day is good for your heart.
ZH: 我们注意保持身体健康，所以经常参加运动。
EN: We pay attention to keeping our bodies healthy, so we exercise regularly.
ZH: 她认为只有靠运动才能保持好身材。
EN: She believes that only exercising can maintain a good figure.
ZH: 运动可以让人精力充沛。
EN: Exercise can make people energetic.
ZH: 昨天我和朋友一起做了很多运动。
EN: I did a lot of exercise with friends yesterday.
ZH: 运动不仅可以强身健体，还可以锻炼意志。
EN: Exercise can not only strengthen the body, but also train the will.
ZH: 好的运动习惯会带来积极的生活方式。
EN: Good exercise habits bring a positive lifestyle.
ZH: 运动是保持身体健康的最佳方式之一。
EN: Exercise is one of the best ways to keep fit.
ZH: 我喜欢户外运动，能让我放松心情。
EN: I enjoy outdoor activities, they help me relax.
ZH: 运动后身体感到疲惫，但精神却很愉快。
EN: The body feels tired after exercise, but the mind is very happy.
